flowchart TD
    A["computeFrontier(tasks, edges)"] --> B["Build executableTaskIds<br />READY | IN_PROGRESS | BLOCKED | DONE"]
    B --> C["Build depsOf map<br />task → tasks it depends on"]
    C --> D["For each non-DONE executable task"]
    D --> E["incomplete = deps.filter<br />d not in doneSet"]
    E --> F{incomplete<br />length?}
    F -->|0| G["frontier.push(task)"]
    F -->|> 0| H["blockedBy.set(task, incomplete)"]
    G & H --> I["Return {frontier sorted, blockedBy}"]
